/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: MD_OLPARAM */
/*==============================================================*/
create table MD_OLPARAM
(
OLPARAMID NUMBER(32) not null,
"OrgID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"OrgCode" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"OrgLevel" INTEGER not null,
"BGColorVal" NVARCHAR2(200),
LNG NUMBER(20,4),
LAT NUMBER(20,4),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CenterLNG" NUMBER(20,4),
"CenterLAT" NUMBER(20,4),
"TileMapLevel" INTEGER,
"ScrollWheelFlag" INTEGER,
"DragEnable" INTEGER,
"DoubleClickZoom" INTEGER,
constraint PK_MD_OLPARAM primary key (OLPARAMID)
);

comment on table MD_OLPARAM is
'区域参数颜色和经纬度设置（分析主题使用）';

comment on column MD_OLPARAM."OrgLevel" is
'1: 总部
2: 大区
3: 小区';

comment on column MD_OLPARAM."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0：无效';

comment on column MD_OLPARAM."ScrollWheelFlag" is
' 0:不支持 1：支持';

comment on column MD_OLPARAM."DragEnable" is
' 0:不支持 1：支持';

comment on column MD_OLPARAM."DoubleClickZoom" is
' 0:不支持 1：支持';
